txt.en: After the War of the Dwarves and Orcs was ended, Orcs returned to Gundabad and laid claim to the countless dwarf-made weapons left abandoned in its halls. Many are now held as trophies by the Orcs of Bekâr-zarakh.
'You've done well to reclaim what was taken from us, [placeholder]! Let us return and report your success to Hórin!'
Your mission is to reclaim dwarf-made weapons held as trophies by the Orcs in Bekâr-zarakh.
